        &lt;identifier&gt;https://api.aiscr.cz/id/M-202204394&lt;/identifier&gt;
        &lt;datestamp&gt;2024-04-26T13:08:37.256Z&lt;/datestamp&gt;
        &lt;setSpec&gt;projekt&lt;/setSpec&gt;
      &lt;/header&gt;
    &lt;/record&gt;
    [...]
